    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> We spent the rest of the day comfortably with splashing, sunbathing, and doing nothing. In the evening, we went to the delicious buffet as usual. This time we even had company: Hauke from Bad Schwartau was sitting at our table. He's alone in Tenerife, and we got into conversation while eating when it turned out that he lives around the corner from us. The world is sometimes small! </p>
        <p> Another sunny and relaxed vacation day comes to an end - that's exactly how we love it. </p>
